<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.5.3">
<l>āḻkaṭalcūḻ vaiyakattā rēcappō yāyppāṭit</l>
<l>tāḻkuḻalār vaitta tayiruṇṭāṉ kāṇēṭī</l>
<l>tāḻkuḻalār vaitta tayiruṇṭa poṉvayiṟiv</l>
<l>vēḻulaku muṇṭu miṭamuṭaittāl cāḻalē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>See, Friend! Reaching the herder village</l>
<l rend="indent">so that those of the deep sea-ringed earth scolded,</l>
<l>He ate up the curds stored by those with dangling curls.</l>
<l>Although the golden belly, which ate up the curds</l>
<l rend="indent">stored by those with dangling curls,</l>
<l>Ate these seven worlds, it [still] had room! Cāḻalē!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
